title: Ep. 1255 - Champaklal In Trouble - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu wakes Daya and Jetha up and informs them about Champaklal getting hiccups. Chacha ji comes and is unable to talk as he is unable to stop the hiccups. Daya suggests a solution to this but doesn't work.

title: Ep. 1256 - Taarak Comes For Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha calls Taarak, informs about Champaklal's never-ending hiccups. Taarak explains to them why the hiccups occur. Taarak asks them to scare him so that he gets rid of hiccups or to divert his attention.

title: Ep. 1257 - Chacha Ji Is Out Of Control - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer comes and asks everyone to make him drink water. Hearing this, Champaklal goes mad and shouts at everyone and tells them he has had enough of water. Iyer gives them a scientific and logical way to get rid of the hiccups.

title: Ep. 1258 - Daya Comes Up With A Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya shares her plan with everyone and Taarak agrees and says they can try it once. Taarak and Iyer lets a dog inside the Gada house. Scared Champaklal runs around the house and gets rid of the hiccups.

title: Ep. 1259 - An Antique Radio - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide finds an antique radio in an old shop and it interests him. Bhide negotiates him for the price as he really wants it. The shop owner tells him that once he sells something, he doesn't take it back.

title: Ep. 1260 - Bhide Reminisces About Childhood - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide is excited to play songs on the radio. He talks about his good old days where he used to listen to songs on a radio that his grandfather had. He asks Madhvi to listen to it once but unfortunately, it doesn't work.

title: Ep. 1261 - Radio Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide tries to fix the radio. Jetha thinks that he is crazy and doesn't know how to fix the radio. Bhide is very stubborn and doesn't wanna sleep till he fixes the radio. Will Bhide fix the radio?

title: Ep. 1262 - The Haunted Radio - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham is hit by weird thunder and lighting. The lightening does something to the radio and it starts making a weird sound. Champaklal wakes up Tappu and tells him about the noise.

title: Ep. 1263 - The UFO  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham was visited by an UFO and everyone is scared. Iyer tries to fix the radio. They decide to keep the radio in the clubhouse. Everyone wants Popatlal to call Hrithik Roshan to Gokuldham.

title: Ep. 1264 - Hrithik Roshan Contacts The Alien - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Hrithik visits Gokuldham and tries to call the UFO again. The alien tries to contact them to pass on a message. Hrithik decodes the messages and tells everyone. The alien wishes a very happy Diwali.

title: Ep. 1265 - Veera Calls Daya - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya misses her brother and wishes to see him. Veera calls her at the right time and makes her happy. She tells him all the Gokuldham's Diwali celebration.

title: Ep. 1266 - Good News For Tappu - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya gets a call from Tappu's cricket coach and he informs her that Tappu is selected as the school's cricket captain. Daya informs Jetha and Champaklal and everyone is delighted.

title: Ep. 1267 - Tappu's Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tappu decides to leave cricket as his idol Sachin left the game. Jetha, Daya, and champaklal come up with the plan to change Tappu's mind and make him play cricket again. Will Tappu ever change his mind?

title: Ep. 1268 - Popatlal's Dream Plan With Sachin - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Men of Gokuldham decide to go to the stadium and watch Tappu's a match. Popatlal has different plans. He dreams of watching Sachin's old matches with Sachin at his house. Will Popatlal's dream come true?

title: Ep. 1269 - Duplicate Tickets - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal tells everyone that the tickets they have are duplicate. Everyone is shocked and doesn't know what to do. They try to inform the police and they arrive. How will the police handle the situation?
